{"type": "root", "attrs": {"helpid": "h.menu.windows.coloreditor"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color Editor"], "extent": [0, 17]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["The color editor is an expanded interface for picking colors."], "extent": [55, 124]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [124, 139], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The Houdini user interface includes color editors that you can configure to further customize ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#color", "type": "link", "text": ["color"], "fullpath": "/ref/windows/coloreditor.html#color", "fragment": "#color"}, " and ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#mono", "type": "link", "text": ["mono ramps"], "fullpath": "/ref/windows/coloreditor.html#mono", "fragment": "#mono"}, "."], "extent": [139, 274]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color wheel"], "extent": [274, 287], "body": [{"type": "table", "thead": [], "body": [{"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 4, "text": [{"keys": ["LMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [287, 301], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Pick a color from wheel"], "extent": [301, 334]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click in the ring around the color wheel "], "role": "td", "extent": [334, 381], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Change only the hue."], "extent": [381, 411]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 4, "text": ["Drag ", {"keys": ["MMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " across color wheel "], "role": "td", "extent": [411, 449], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Change the HSV value in small increments."], "extent": [449, 500]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 4, "text": ["Drag ", {"keys": ["RMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " across color wheel "], "role": "td", "extent": [500, 538], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Change the HSV value in larger increments."], "extent": [538, 590]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 4, "text": ["Hold ", {"keys": ["T"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, ", ", {"keys": ["M"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, ", ", {"keys": ["I"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, ", ", {"keys": ["R"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, ", ", {"keys": ["G"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, ", or ", {"keys": ["B"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " while dragging "], "role": "td", "extent": [590, 660], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Change only one of the sliders."], "extent": [660, 701]}]}], "divider": false}]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color sliders"], "extent": [701, 716], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The color sliders let you choose colors using different component models: TMI (temperature, magenta, intensity), HSV (hue, saturation, value), and RGB (red, green, blue)."], "extent": [716, 892]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["TMI can be a convenient model for certain cinematic/photographic color operations. For example, in RGB you might increase red and decrease blue to warm the color, or increase blue and decrease red to cool it. In the TMI model, this is one slider, temperature. Intensity is also useful because it ", {"type": "q", "text": ["brightens"]}, " or ", {"type": "q", "text": ["dulls"]}, " a color while still retaining the color\u2019s ", {"type": "q", "text": ["character"]}, "."], "extent": [892, 1271]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/colors", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/colors.html"}, "\nShow color presets"], "extent": [1271, 1318], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Shows the palette of preset colors."], "extent": [1318, 1359]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/chooser_image_color", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/chooser_image_color.html"}, "\nShow image picker"], "extent": [1359, 1418], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Shows the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#image", "type": "link", "text": ["image color picker"], "fullpath": "/ref/windows/coloreditor.html#image", "fragment": "#image"}, "."], "extent": [1418, 1462]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/dynamic_tmi_sliders", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/dynamic_tmi_sliders.html"}, "\n", {"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/dynamic_rgb_sliders", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/dynamic_rgb_sliders.html"}, "\nDynamic TMI/RGB sliders"], "extent": [1462, 1567], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["When dynamic sliders are off, the colors displayed in the background of the sliders do not update as you edit the color."], "extent": [1567, 1693]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/gamma", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/gamma.html"}, "\nColor correction"], "extent": [1693, 1737], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["When color correction is off, the colors in the interface are not gamma corrected."], "extent": [1737, 1825]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color preset palette"], "extent": [1825, 1847], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The palette of preset colors. For more information, see ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#preset", "type": "link", "text": ["Color preset palette"], "fullpath": "/ref/windows/coloreditor.html#preset", "fragment": "#preset"}, "."], "extent": [1847, 1940]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": ["View/Pick/Input/Display"], "extent": [1940, 1965], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The OpenColorIO color profiles. View and Display affect the display of the color, while Pick and Input affect the picked color."], "extent": [1965, 2102]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Pick is the color space in which you want the picked color. Input is the color space of the input color, the numbers you input, or the picked color from the palette."], "extent": [2102, 2277]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "TOOLS/eyedropper", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/TOOLS/eyedropper.html"}, "\nPick color from screen"], "extent": [2277, 2330], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the icon, then click anywhere in a Houdini window."], "extent": [2330, 2392]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/color_temperature", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/color_temperature.html"}, "\nBlackbody temperature"], "extent": [2392, 2453], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["To choose a temperature from the menu, ", {"keys": ["RMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " the icon and choose a preset option."], "extent": [2453, 2543]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["To enter an exact temperature in degrees Kelvin, ", {"keys": ["RMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " the icon and choose ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Custom"]}, "."], "extent": [2543, 2637]}], "container": true}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [2637, 2646], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["To enter an exact temperature in degrees Kelvin for a non-mono color editor, you can also click the icon."], "extent": [2646, 2761]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Smallicon", "value": "BUTTONS/secondary_colors", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/secondary_colors.html"}, "\nSecondary colors"], "extent": [2761, 2816], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["You can display a small palette of ", {"type": "q", "text": ["secondary"]}, " colors based on different selection methods (for example, complementary colors). These colors change dynamically as you change the current color."], "extent": [2816, 3014]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["To display secondary colors (for example, complementary colors), under the Previous and Current color swatches, click the Show secondary colors menu and choose a color scheme."], "extent": [3014, 3197]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Use the slider under the secondary color swatches to adjust the color spread."], "extent": [3197, 3282]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click one of the colors in the secondary color swatches to make it the current color."], "extent": [3282, 3375]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "color", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color editor"], "extent": [3375, 3402], "body": [{"type": "task_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Open the color editor for a color ramp"], "role": "item", "extent": [3402, 3449], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["In the parameter editor, double-click a point\u2019s arrow-shaped point handle on the bottom of the ramp."], "extent": [3449, 3555]}], "container": true}, {"ext": null, "type": "task", "indent": 0, "text": ["Open the color editor for a color parameter"], "role": "item", "extent": [3555, 3606], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["In the parameter editor, click the color swatch to the right of a color parameter."], "extent": [3606, 3694]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/ui/color_editor_anno.png", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [3694, 3736]}, {"level": 3, "id": "image", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Picking colors from an image"], "extent": [3736, 3781], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["In the top right, click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "BUTTONS/chooser_image_color", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/chooser_image_color.html"}, " Image color picker icon to switch to an interface for picking colors from an image."], "extent": [3781, 3930]}, {"type": "table", "thead": [], "body": [{"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Icon", "value": "BUTTONS/chooser_file", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/chooser_file.html"}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [3930, 3960], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Choose the image file to display."], "extent": [3960, 3999]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Icon", "value": "BUTTONS/reload", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/windows/BUTTONS/reload.html"}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [3999, 4023], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Reload the image from disk."], "extent": [4023, 4056]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"keys": ["LMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [4056, 4066], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Pick a color from the image."], "extent": [4066, 4104]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"keys": ["Shift", "LMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [4104, 4122], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Draw a rectangle around an area of the image. Picks the average of the colors inside the rectangle."], "extent": [4122, 4227]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"keys": ["Alt", "LMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [4227, 4243], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Copies a texture reference expression into the parameters you're editing instead of literal color values."], "extent": [4243, 4354]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"keys": ["MMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [4354, 4364], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Pan around the image."], "extent": [4364, 4391]}]}], "divider": false}, {"type": "row", "body": [{"type": "cell", "indent": 0, "text": [{"keys": ["RMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " or ", {"keys": ["mouse_wheel"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " "], "role": "td", "extent": [4391, 4420], "container": true}, {"type": "cell", "role": "td", "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Zoom in/out on the image."], "extent": [4420, 4455]}]}], "divider": false}]}]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "mono", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Mono color editor"], "extent": [4455, 4486], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The mono col